                        <sf/>
                        <pf/>
                    </name>
                    <name>
                        <ln>Bowman</ln>
                        <fn>Frank</fn>
                        <sf/>
                        <pf>Rev.</pf>
                    </name>
                </names>
                <summary>William N. Willson and Miss Mary V. Poague, daughter of James Poague, were
                    married on May 7th by the Rev. Frank Bowman. Both bride and groom are from
                    Augusta.</summary>
                <note/>
                <look/>
            </div>
            <div type="o">
                <column>02</column>
                <head>Deaths</head>
                <origin/>
                <commentary/>
